* Dried 'Tangerine' Peel, Chenpi (陈皮), 3g or about three pieces
* Garlic, one head, ~70g
* Salt, 1 tsp
* Fermented black soybeans, Douchi (豆豉), 2 tbsp, ~15g
* Shallots (干葱), 2, ~130g
* Sugar, 3 tbsp
* Chicken bouillon powder (鸡粉), 1 tsp -or- MSG (味精), 1/2 tsp
* Oyster sauce (蚝油), 2 tbsp
* Soy sauce (生抽), 1 tbsp
